  <h1>Code of Conduct</h1>
  <div class="legal-divider"></div>
  <p>Ace Strategies is committed to the highest standards of professional conduct in all our activities. This code guides how we engage with clients, government, media, and the community.</p>

  <h2>Integrity and Honesty</h2>
  <p>We act with integrity in all our professional dealings. We provide honest counsel to our clients, even when that advice may be difficult to hear. We do not knowingly mislead clients, government, or the public.</p>

  <h2>Transparency</h2>
  <p>We are transparent about our role, our clients, and our objectives when engaging with government and public institutions. We comply with all applicable lobbying disclosure requirements.</p>

  <h2>Conflicts of Interest</h2>
  <p>We identify and manage conflicts of interest proactively. Where a conflict arises that cannot be managed, we will decline or withdraw from the relevant engagement.</p>

  <h2>Respect and Professionalism</h2>
  <p>We treat all individuals with respect and dignity, regardless of their background, position, or views. We conduct ourselves professionally at all times.</p>

  <h2>Confidentiality</h2>
  <p>We protect the confidential information of our clients and do not disclose such information without authorisation, except where required by law.</p>

  <h2>Compliance</h2>
  <p>We comply with all applicable laws, regulations, and professional standards. We do not engage in, facilitate, or condone corrupt practices of any kind.</p>

  <h2>Community and Environment</h2>
  <p>We consider the broader impact of our work on the community and environment. We support initiatives that contribute to the wellbeing of the communities in which we operate.</p>

  <p>If you have questions about our Code of Conduct, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="color:var(--sky-blue);">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
